'''Madagaskar''', walima '''Madagaskar ka Fasojamana''' (tɔgɔ kɔrɔlen '''Malagasy Fasojamana''', Franse: ''République malgache'') ye jigun manto ye [[India Kɔgɔji]] kɔnɔ Afrika worodugu dankan fɛ, dunia jigun labonba naninan don, dunia jiriw ani feɳama shiw 5% so don, o mina 80% ka surun shilatunu la Madagaskar. O beganw la, sennanimafenw b'a la, sogodunfenw, kɔɔnɔ du saba ani zira shi wɔrɔ. Jamanaden tlasabanan fla bɛ balo jenselekenani fantaya ci jukɔrɔ n'o ye dolar wari US$ 1.25 don kɔnɔ.
